social_posts.post_text: This day is bittersweet. We will forever cherish the friendships and memories made in West TX, but life is taking us on a new  adventure. Maybe someday we will be back but hopefully not! 😅 STAY WILD 🫶🫶🫶

Take care of those smiles y’all! McRae Dental keeps my smile in tip top shape! They are by far the best dental office in the Treasure Valley! They’ll take great care of you and they provide everything from regular cleanings to veneers and major dental work! I’m blessed to be a part of the McRae dental family and I promise you won’t regret giving them a call! 🦷❤️
